title: Happy Hour #50: Too Much
itunes:title: Happy Hour #50: Too Much
description:
Ever left a party and wanted to shrink and disappear and apologize to everyone you've ever met for your very existence? Yep, it's that episode. Samantha and Anney share very different perspectives but similar reactions to the same party.
